title: Ep. #125 | Catching Up: UMI
description:
You know that feeling when you catch up with a friend who you haven't seen in a while, and the conversation is, if not more, just as spectacular? THIS. IS. THAT. EPISODE. Daebak listeners, please welcome UMI! Hear about UMI's upbringing, goal manifesting, and 'Introspection'. This is the auditory hug you didn't know you needed.
